description:
An evil Lich has tainted Mama Duck’s beloved pond and kidnapped her ducklings!

Arm up and beat him once and for all in this QuackMan roguelite - storm through dungeon mazes to rescue her family!

With classic arcade controls and a twist - an attack button that lets you smash walls and enemies – you’ll fight back against the Lich and his army in no time!

- Forge your own path through the maze;
- Battle massive bosses and fight back a wide variety of undead minions;
- Make animal friends;
- FASHION DUCKS! Compose gear combinations for Mama Duck and her duck-chain!
